OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs to flat will get new home
OL,6,FA father who was forced to carry his
OL,7,Fdisabled son up a flight of stairs to
OL,8,Ftheir first floor flat is to move into
OL,9,Fa new adapted home.
OL,11,FStephen Murray was living with four
OL,12,Fsons in his one bedroom flat where
OL,13,Fthey are all had to sleep in the same
OL,14,Froom.
OL,16,FAfter his story was featured on ITV
OL,17,FGranada Reports, the family were moved
OL,18,Finto hotel accommodation and told
OL,19,Fthere was a property they could move
OL,20,Finto that is being adapted to their
OL,21,Fneeds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
