OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs to flat will get new home
OL,6,FIt is a four-bedroomed house and
OL,7,Fassessments will be carried out on
OL,8,Fwhether seven-year-old Harry, who has
OL,9,Fcerebral palsy, will be able to use
OL,10,Fthe stairlift to access a wet room or
OL,11,Fif an adapted lift will be needed.
OL,13,FStephen said he had been "despairing"
OL,14,Fliving in the cramped flat in Widnes,
OL,15,FCheshire, and worried about how long
OL,16,Fhe would be able to carry Harry
OL,17,Fupstairs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
