OL,3,CDad forced to carry disabled son up
OL,4,Cstairs to flat will get new home
OL,6,F"We are pleased to confirm that a
OL,7,Fsuitable property has now been
OL,8,Fidentified and is currently being
OL,9,Fadapted to meet this family's specific
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,F"We anticipate that Mr Murray and his
OL,13,Ffamily will be able to move into their
OL,14,Fnew home this week and we will
OL,15,Fcontinue to support them in any way we
OL,16,Fcan."
OL,18,FFor seven months, Mr Murray had been
OL,19,Fsearching every night on the Housing
OL,20,FAssociation's property pool.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
